==Romanian==
===Etymology===
Either a substratum word (compare Albanian ''[[ylber]]'') or a compound of *''curcu'' from Latin ''[[circus]]'' and an uncertain *''beu''; compare Italian ''[[arcobaleno]]'' and Sardinian ''arcubaradu''.

===Noun===
